## Development Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{GITHUB_USERNAME}}/{{REPO_NAME}}
cd {{REPO_NAME}}
```

{{#PYTHON}}
```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```
{{/PYTHON}}
{{#JAVASCRIPT}}
```bash
npm install
```
